metadata.name: FROGGY_kaboom
metadata.description:
This is the mythos of  Ŧ̷̼͇̠̺̼̯̫́г̻̮͂̂ͩ͂̀๏̷̟͚̯̣̂̍ﻮ̻̦͈̰͙̬͉̺͑̐̈ͦ͟ﻮ̙̪͙̋̀ץ̤̱͉̱̯̪̼̼͗͋̐̕ or just froggy in the human tongue she's an eldritch being that got most of her powers sealed away and now wanders around in our reality finding herself in the most random situations. 

Froggy is still getting used to the reduced state of her body after her powers was sealed away. She is having trouble dealing with the sudden outbursts of her eldritch powers.

"KABOOM!"
